<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278670>
    dc:description "PLATE 83. Dryinus pyrilliivorus. A. Female from Thailand. Length 4.0 mm. B. Head of female (holotype of Richardsidryinus gauldi) (from Olmi 1987c). C. Vertex of holotype (from Olmi 1986). D. Chela of holotype (from Olmi 1986). E. Female from China, Zhejiang (from He & Xu, 2002). F. Male genitalia. Scale bar 1.67 mm for B, 1.23 mm for C, 0.33 mm for D, 0.31 mm for E, 0.20 mm for F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278670/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

